Wanted to buy Spaceballs, saw this combo and thought it a great steal for 3 great films so I bought it.  No issues with shipping.  However upon receipt, I went to put in the Spaceballs disc and it would neither go to the menu screen nor would it play the movie.  It instead sits on a black screen.  Other 2 discs are fine and work as expected, but I am super annoyed that the only one I really wanted does not work.  Will be returning.
